title: Geisha Stories (Kenji Mizoguchi + BBC) Japanese with English sub
description:
2 quite different films (from 1936 and 1953) set in Gion, 
the Geisha quarter in Kyoto, both made by Japanese director 
Kenji Mizoguchi. 
www.imdb.com/title/tt0027672/ (from 1936)
www.imdb.com/title/tt0045814/ (from 1953)

The BBC documentary (2005) shows the daily life of an young woman 
who aspires to become a geisha/geiko after years of training.
www.imdb.com/title/tt0843273/
